{"lemma":"مُدْرِكُو","slug":"مُدْرِكُو","root":"د.ر.ك","root_slug":"د-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُدْرِك","root":"درك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12472","n12473","n12474"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%83%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of أَدْرَكَ (ʔadraka).","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"who reaches, who attains"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"who perceives, who comprehends"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"perceptive"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"passive participle of أَدْرَكَ (ʔadraka).","tags":["form-of","participle","passive"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"perceived"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb أَدْرَكَ (ʔadraka).\n\nDerived from the passive participle of the verb أَدْرَكَ (ʔadraka)."},"ipa":["/mud.rik/","/mud.rak/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12472","headword_ar":"مَدْرَكٌ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudorakN","text_ar":"مُدْرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu madorakN","text_ar":"لَهُ مَدْرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if not a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudorikN","text_ar":"مُدْرِكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudorakN","text_ar":"مُدْرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has a sense in excess;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a preternatural perception,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a second sight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diraAkapN","text_ar":"دِرَاكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12473","headword_ar":"مُدْرَكٌ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a time, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAkN","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attaining, reaching, overtaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (Msb.) Hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"madaAriku Al$~aroEi","text_ar":"مَدَارِكُ الشَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, Msb;) among which is included investigation of the law by means of reason and comparison; (Mgh;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sources from which are sought the ordinances of the law; where one seeks for guidance by means of texts"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Kur-án or the Sunneh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and by means of investigation by reason and comparison:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) the lawyers make the sing. to be ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"madorakN","text_ar":"مَدْرَكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, * Msb;) but there is no way of resolving this: (Msb:) correctly, by rule, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudorakN","text_ar":"مُدْرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because the meaning intended is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAk","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  [Also pass. part. n. of 4. ―         -b3-  And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Perceived by means of any of the senses;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHosuwsN","text_ar":"مَحْسُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perceived by the intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHosuwsN","text_ar":"مَحْسُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n12474","headword_ar":"مُدْرِكٌ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~aAkN","text_ar":"دَرَّاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alquw~apu Almudorikapu","text_ar":"القُوَّةُ المُدْرِكَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and simply"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almudorikapu","text_ar":"المُدْرِكَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as a subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The perceptive faculty of the mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"See also what next follows.]"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}